WEBVTT

00:00.211 --> 00:02.095
<i>Previously on</i> Camelot...

00:02.120 --> 00:05.518
Do you really think that the
king will not wonder where I am?

00:06.011 --> 00:07.878
Are you sure
this is what you want?

00:07.946 --> 00:10.114
You said I'd been
given the gift for a reason.

00:10.182 --> 00:13.809
Now I know what it is.

00:13.877 --> 00:17.269
- It's good to be home.
- Yes. It is.

00:17.337 --> 00:22.029
You are a good man, Leontes,
with a big enough heart to forgive.

00:22.096 --> 00:25.523
- What do I have to forgive?
- Arthur and Guinevere--

00:25.590 --> 00:29.311
what happened between them
on your wedding day.

00:29.379 --> 00:31.174
I could be more open.

00:31.242 --> 00:33.374
You can always practice
with me.

00:33.442 --> 00:35.540
I have nothing
to hide.

00:35.607 --> 00:37.035
You are to recruit some men.

00:37.102 --> 00:40.433
You will attack the outpost
at Barden Pass.

00:40.501 --> 00:42.397
This will draw out the king.

00:42.465 --> 00:46.193
I am the king's mother!
Do you understand what will happen

00:46.261 --> 00:49.090
when he finds out
what's been done to me?

00:51.492 --> 00:55.554
♪

